# π²

> [π][@stdlib/math/constants/float64-pi]².

<section class="usage">

## Usage

``` javascript
var PI_SQUARED = require( '@stdlib/math/constants/float64-pi-squared' );
```

#### PI_SQUARED

Square of the mathematical constant [π][@stdlib/math/constants/float64-pi].

``` javascript
PI_SQUARED === 9.869604401089358;
```

</section>

<!-- /.usage -->
